<div class="detail-container">
	<div class="detail-info-box">
		<div class="detail-info">
			<ul>
				<li class="detail-product-name">Product Name</li>
			</ul>
			<ul>
				<li class="detail-price-info">&#36; Price Info</li>
			</ul>
			<i id="heart" class="fa fa-heart-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
		</div>
		<div class="detail-info">
			<ul>
				<li class="info-category">size</li>
				<li class="info-val">265mm</li>
			</ul>
			<ul>
				<li class="info-category">Quality</li>
				<li class="info-val">새상품</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="detail-info">
			<ul>
				<li class="info-category">Seller</li>
				<li class="info-val"><i class="fa fa-star" aria-hidden="true"></i>수현이당</li>
			</ul>
			<ul>
				<li class="info-category">판매완료</li>
				<li class="info-val">총 3건</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="detail-info">
			<ul>
				<li class="info-category">Details</li>
				<li class="info-val">제품 판매 사유 / 구매날자 / 워런티 보유 / 취급방법 등</li>
