			</ul>
			<ul>
				<li class="trade-method">택배거래</li>
				<li>택배비 착불</li>
			</ul>
			<ul>
				<li class="trade-method">안심거래</li>
				<li>가능</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<button type="button" class="buy-button">구매</button>

	<div class="comment-box-container">
